      <T n="text">0xA6A927A4<!--String: "Do you enjoy the thrill of a <b><font color='#199C2C'>romantic affair</font></b>? If your Sim already has an official partner (whose Romantic Boundaries are set to allow for jealousy)...you may now get yourself a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Secret Lover</font></b> too!\n\nSecret Lovers behave similarly to other romantic partners, but they will be more careful <b><font color='#199C2C'>not to flirt with your Sim in front of their <i>official</i> family</font></b>. To establish a Secret Lover, develop your <b><font color='#199C2C'>romance bar</font></b> with another Sim, then select them, choose the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationship</font></b> category, and select the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Ask to be Secret Lover</font></b> interaction.\n\nHaving a Secret Lover can be titillating, but watch out—getting very close romantically may occasionally lead the Secret Lover to feel jealousy for your Sim's official partner!"--></T>
